loadFrames.desc:
Loads frames into sprite.  
`spr` - sprite to load frames into.  
`img` - path to the image.  
`type` - type of the spritesheet. Spritesheet types:  
`texture`, `textureatlas`, `tex`;  
`texture_noaa`, `textureatlas_noaa`, `tex_noaa`;  
`packer`, `packeratlas`, `pac`;  
Defaults to `sparrow`.

makeAnimatedLuaSprite.desc:
Makes an animated sprite with the given tag, image and position.  
If sprite with that tag already exists, it gets replaced.  
`image` - path to the image like `bg-stuff/goober`.  
`type` - spritesheet data type:  
`texture`, `textureatlas`, `tex`;  
`texture_noaa`, `textureatlas_noaa`, `tex_noaa`;  
`packer`, `packeratlas`, `pac`;  
Defaults to `sparrow`.

